<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśubhajātakābhyude
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ya śakavarṣaṁbulu 1359 Agunē
<lb n="3" break="no"/><unclear>ṭi</unclear> piṁgaḷasaṁvatsara caitra śu 15
<lb n="4"/>gu sa<unclear>rva</unclear>lōkāśraya śrīviṣṇuva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rdhanamahārājulai caṁdravaṁśyu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>lai Upēṁdradēvacakravarttulaku
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nnu Atyamāṁbakunnu suputṛlai
<lb n="8" break="no"/>na śrīnarasiṁhyadēvacakravartulu
<lb n="9"/>paramēśvaraprītigānunnu tamakunu
<lb n="10"/>Āyurārōgyaiśvaryyābhivṛdhdhigā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nunnupaṁcadhā<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied>la dharmēśvaramahāliṁgā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>naku raṁgabhōgānakai samarpaṇacēyabaḍḍa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>kṣētraṁ mā Oḍḍalapolamulōnu mūḍu vu
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṭlunnu velusūri pōlamulōnu puṭṭeḍu
<lb n="15"/>Ī kṣētra manubhaviṁci dēvaraṁ goliciḍi sānulu
<lb n="16"/>narasiṁhyadēvacakravartula bhōgastrī vīrakkagā
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ri kūṁtulu buḍḍesāni nūṁkasāninni golavā
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ḍa pōtunaṭṭavuni kūṁtuṟu tallasāninni pō
<lb n="19" break="no"/>lagaṁgasāninni Aṁgabhōga mamṛtamaṇi
<lb n="20" break="no"/>kaipeṁkalapāṭi Uttarānanu kaluvalapallipā
<lb n="21" break="no"/>ṭi paṁdumu kṣētraṁ peṭṭiri <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

